Third-party attribution notes (not covered by this MIT license):

  * Player photos served from Wikipedia REST API are licensed under their
    respective Wikipedia licenses (CC BY-SA / public domain / etc.). They are
    fetched at runtime via the public API and are NOT bundled with this
    repository.

  * Country flag images are served from FlagCDN (CC0). They are fetched at
    runtime and not bundled.

  * Champion taglines included in this software are original tributes to the
    Chinese sports-broadcasting tradition. They are NOT quotations of any
    specific commentator's work and any resemblance to existing commentary is
    coincidental or in the realm of common classical-Chinese phrasing.

  * Player roster data reflects 2024-2025 national-team squad snapshots
    compiled from public information.
